description:
GRAPE is the Ethereum token that was produced by the development
members of coingrape.io(following, coingrape). Coingrape is a web service
that enables to collect and compare the evaluations of AirDrop. You will be
able to collect and list evaluation values in a list from various sites and see
the evaluations from each site at a glance. By doing this, we will support you
more smart investments quickly.
name: GRAPE
